title: Bolado's Sucos
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Juice and sandwich bar offers menu items for vegans such as juices and smoothies. Vegans try the berinjela temperada/eggplant sandwich. Sandwich bread choices include wheat, oat, bagette, carrot or ciabata. Drinks include energy, vitamin, tropical mixes. Also serves fruit and green salads. Has various locations around town - check their website.
